                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="1r" to="8v" facs="004"/><title>Chants called Mästägabǝ’, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መስተጋብዕ፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ወለቡ፡ ጽራኅየ፡ ወአጽምአኒ፡ ቃለ፡ ስዕለትየ፡ ከመ፡ ወልታ፡ ስሙር፡ ከለልከነ፡ እግዚኦ፡ እግዚኦ፡ በመዓትከ፡ ኢትቅሥፈኒ፡ ወበመቅሠፍትከ፡ ኢትገሥጸኒ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="8v" to="15r" facs="012"/><title>Chants called Arba’ǝt, <foreign xml:lang="gez">አርባዕት</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ቃልየ፡ አጽምዕ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ወለቡ፡ ጽራኅየ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ወአጽምአኒ፡ ቃለ፤ ስዕለትየ፡ ንጉሥየኒ፤ ወአምላኪየኒ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>(also called Qalǝyä)</note>
                </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3"><locus from="15r" to="22v" facs="018"/><title>Chants called Aryam, <foreign xml:lang="gez">አርያም፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ለአብ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ለወልድ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ወለመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ቀዳሚ፡ ዜማ፡ ግበሩ፡ በዓለ፡ በትፍሥሕት፡ እስከ፡ አቅርንቲሁ፡ ለምስዋዕ፡ ዛቲ፡ ፋሲካ፡ ቀዳሚት፡ ሕግ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4"><locus from="22v" to="38r" facs="026"/><title>Chants called Śäläst, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሠለስት፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">፫ ስምዓኒ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ጸሎትየ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ወይብጻሕ፡ ቅድሜከ፡ ገአርየ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5"><locus from="38r" to="48r" facs="041"/><title>Chants called Kǝśtät, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክሥተት፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ይትፌሣሕ፡ ልሳንየ፡ በጽድቀ፡ ዚአከ፡ ትከሥት፡ ከናፍርየ፡ ወአፉየ፡ ያየድአ፡ ስብሐቲከ። <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
